media:group.media:description:
HEY EVERYONE.. Welcome BACK to my channel!! Today I'm so excited to introduce you to the newest member for the Star Family!!!! I was ready to expand and felt in my heart we needed one more Pomeranian to add to our home. Welcome number 8, little Drizzle Lynn Star!!! He was born Nov. 3rd 2021 and he's my 3rd Scorpio dog! He's definitely the life of the party here at the Star YaK Ranch and is fitting in perfect! Come meet him and also get some major life updates about me! I've secretly had Drizzle for a few months so after you meet him, you'll see me jet-set off to beautiful Paris, France were I went to attend Virgil's last Louis Vuitton runway show. What a magical experience.
